<h1>Articles</h1>

Our blog has <%= Article.public_count %> public articles and counting! <br>
<%= Article.archived_count %> articles are in our archives.

<ul>
  <% @articles.each do |article| %>
    <% unless article.archived? %>
      <li>
        <%= link_to article.title, article %>
      </li>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<%= link_to "New Article", new_article_path %>
